title: VideoHive - Kremlin
description:
Kremlin is a CS4/5 after effects template with great dynamics and a nice russian vintage style. it has great rhythm with fast cuts and fast transitions. You can use it as an tv show or movie opener or even as a very stylized photo slide. You can easily change the color of the monochromatic photos and creat really interesting looks The project uses PARTICULAR 2.0 for the little letters in the background.

Information: http://videohive.net/item/kremlin/1811458
